name: Embed Google Datastudio
author: Elangovan A

sections.description:
The Embed Google Datastudio plugin is using for embedding the google data studio report into our WordPress page and also admin panel.Admin or user can view the report created in Google datastudio.

Major features in Embed google datastudio:

  • User can embed the google datastdio report into admin panel
  • By generating the shortcode dynamically user can embed the report any page
  • User can manage the more than one report in admin panel
  • User can view report WordPress admin panel itself instead of Google Datastudio application page.
sections.installation:
1. Upload embed-google-data-studio folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
  3. Insert the shortcode required pages as you need.
